page.content: Other pressures will undoubtably rear their heads in the future as people continue to become more numerous,more mobile,and more sophisticated in their demands.In particular,demands on this areas'water based recreation facilities;the River Yare and Rockland Broad,for example.A further feature of the area is the high level of car ownership,not surprising considering its remoteless,and the numbers of people that have to travel to work. Rail and bus service remain dispite the growth of car ownership and are reasonably frequent.
